 bankruptcy in November, its=C2=A0current equity value is $0, and SoftBank =
has torched its multibillion-dollar investment.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-=
bottom: 5px;">But Neumann still has=C2=A0<em>his=C2=A0</em>money, and he cl=
